caption: For the amount of customers I’ve seen at the various times I’ve been at this location, the crew members and management, while overworked, provide amazing service every single time. I hope their management or corporate will provide them with the help they need, because while they all work tirelessly towards providing phenomenal customer service, they all seem tired and visibly stressed. While I give 5 stars for customer service, I give 0 stars for treatment of employees and will personally never order from Chipotle again to at least help all those wonderful people where their corporate management has failed them.
